- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of NLP models for automatic feedback generation and data annotation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques to improve the central model. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning for data annotation and feedback generation. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper discusses the potential impact of the system on education and training in different professions. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the interactive approach of the system and its potential benefits for both students and instructors.
